    b" and remembered\x0a          context.\x0a        - Preserve the user's goal, useful wo"
    b"rding, preferences, constraints, and\x0a          unresolved details explicitly pre"
    b"sent in the supplied context.\x0a        - Translate remembered context into concre"
    b"te task-relevant guidance.\x0a        - Keep task_input concise and natural. Use li"
    b"ght bullets when they make it\x0a          easier to read.\x0a        - Write for the "
    b"task runner using human-meaningful context rather than\x0a          source bookkeep"
    b"ing.\x0a        - Set candidate_memory only when this composition step reveals dura"
